  <brief_title>Levosimendan and Myocardial Protection</brief_title>
  <official_title>Levosimendan Pre-Treatment in Patients Undergoing Coronary Artery Bypass Graft Surgery: a Double-Blind, Single Center, Prospective, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled Trial</official_title>
