  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to investigate whether pharmacological pre-treatment with
      levosimendan reduces intensive care unit (ICU) length of stay in patients undergoing elective
      myocardial revascularization under cardiopulmonary bypass.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
